239
00:33:44,338 --> 00:33:45,999
Jonathan.

240
00:33:48,042 --> 00:33:50,203
Jonathan!

241
00:33:55,817 --> 00:33:57,284
Dad.

242
00:33:59,454 --> 00:34:00,819
No!

243
00:34:04,192 --> 00:34:06,126
