248
00:37:58,225 --> 00:38:01,023
Clark, get up.

249
00:38:04,465 --> 00:38:06,729
Good morning, Smiley.

250
00:38:07,835 --> 00:38:10,429
Clark, breakfast.

251
00:38:13,708 --> 00:38:16,700
